OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FKeir Starmer said it was "staggering"
OL,7,Fand "unforgivable" that he wasn't told
OL,8,Fformer US Ambassador Lord Mandelson
OL,9,Fhad failed to pass security vetting,
OL,10,Fas ITV News Political Correspondent
OL,11,FShehab Khan explains.
OL,13,FWords by ITV News Producer Kieran
OL,14,FCarter
OL,16,FOn Thursday, April 16, it was reported
OL,17,Fthat Peter Mandelson had failed his
OL,18,Fsecurity vetting when applying for the
OL,19,Frole of Washington ambassador early in
OL,20,F2025.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
