PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FIt was reported that despite UK
OL,7,FSecurity Vetting (UKSV) assessing that
OL,8,Fhe posed a risk to national security,
OL,9,Fofficials in the Foreign Office
OL,10,Foverruled the advice to grant him
OL,11,Fclearance anyway.
OL,13,FAll roles in the Civil Service require
OL,14,Fsome level of vetting, but what is
OL,15,Finvolved and why did Mandelson
OL,16,Freportedly fail it?
OL,18,FWhat is Vetting?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FAll roles in the civil service require
OL,7,Fsome level of vetting, and depending
OL,8,Fon the information they will be asked
OL,9,Fto handle, they may require higher or
OL,10,Flower levels of clearance.
OL,12,FThe government says vetting procedures
OL,13,Fallow it to ensure "everyone with
OL,14,Faccess to protectively marked material
OL,15,Fhas a high level of integrity, and is
OL,16,Funlikely to be blackmailed or
OL,17,Fextorted."
OL,19,FThe three levels of government
OL,20,Finformation are classed as:
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FSeveral tiers of vetting exist, with
OL,7,Fhigher levels of clearance being
OL,8,Frequired by those with access to
OL,9,Fhigher levels of information. These
OL,10,Fare:
OL,12,FBaseline Personnel Security Standard
OL,13,F(BPSS) - The lowest level of vetting,
OL,14,Frequired by anyone with access to
OL,15,Fgovernment assets, such as civil
OL,16,Fservants and members of the armed
OL,17,Fforces. This level of clearance
OL,18,Fincludes identity checks, right to
OL,19,Fwork checks, employment history and
OL,20,Funspent criminal record checks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FCounter Terrorist Check (CTC) -
OL,7,FRequired by those working closely with
OL,8,F"at-risk" public figures, those with
OL,9,Faccess to information that would be
OL,10,Fvaluable to terrorists, and those with
OL,11,Faccess to locations like parliament
OL,12,Fthat would be of value to terrorists.
OL,13,FThis level of clearance requires
OL,14,Fpassing everything included in BPSS
OL,15,Fchecks, as well as a security
OL,16,Fquestionnaire, a check of security
OL,17,Fservice records, and a check of spent
OL,18,Fcriminal records.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FSecurity Check (SC) - Required by
OL,7,Fthose with unsupervised access to
OL,8,Fgovernment information classed as
OL,9,Fsecret, and supervised access to
OL,10,Finformation classified as top secret.
OL,11,FThis level requires completion of all
OL,12,Fthe above categories as well as checks
OL,13,Fof the applicant's credit and
OL,14,Ffinancial history. It is also possible
OL,15,Fthat a full review of personal
OL,16,Ffinances and checks of relatives or
OL,17,Findividuals mentioned in the security
OL,18,Fquestionnaire could be required.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FDeveloped Vetting (DV) - Required for
OL,7,Fthose needing regular unsupervised
OL,8,Faccess to top secret government
OL,9,Finformation. This level of clearance
OL,10,Frequires all of the above, as well as
OL,11,Fa full review of personal finances, an
OL,12,Finterview with a vetting officer, and
OL,13,Finterviews with referees who know the
OL,14,Fapplicant well. Interviews involve the
OL,15,Fdetailed disclosure and verification
OL,16,Fof personal history, including issues
OL,17,Fsuch as relationships and drug use.
OL,19,FWhat does Developed Vetting include?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
