OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FThe role of Washington ambassador
OL,7,Frequires the highest level of security
OL,8,Fclearance, and it is this developed
OL,9,Fvetting Mandelson is said to have
OL,10,Ffailed to receive before the decision
OL,11,Fwas reportedly overturned by the
OL,12,FForeign Office.
OL,14,FThe government says this level of
OL,15,Fvetting includes "uncomfortable
OL,16,Fquestions on sexual history and
OL,17,Fpreferences, drug and alcohol use",
OL,18,Fand questions about an individual's
OL,19,Fconsumption of pornography.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
