PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FThese questions can also include an
OL,7,Fapplicant's use of dating apps and
OL,8,Fgambling.
OL,10,FIt is up to the individual to disclose
OL,11,Finformation when asked - something the
OL,12,Fprime minister claims Peter Mandelson
OL,13,Fdid not do.
OL,15,FThe civil service says: "At its core,
OL,16,Fthe DV process is about seeing if
OL,17,Fwe're comfortable with allowing access
OL,18,Fto the most sensitive information that
OL,19,Fwe hold.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
