OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,F"If you choose not to disclose
OL,7,Fsomething that comes to light later,
OL,8,Fit might not change the outcome of
OL,9,Fyour vetting, but it might raise a few
OL,10,Fquestions around your integrity."
