OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FThe reasons Mandelson failed security
OL,7,Fvetting are not known, but officials
OL,8,Fsay it is rare for individuals to do
OL,9,Fso.
OL,11,FSeveral potential security risks and
OL,12,Fconflicts of interest were raised
OL,13,Fbefore Mandelson was appointed in a
OL,14,Fdue diligence report, which was seen
OL,15,Fby the prime minister.
OL,17,FThese included his relationship with
OL,18,FJeffrey Epstein and publicly reported
OL,19,Flinks to both Russia and China.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
