OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FIn September, it was reported by The
OL,7,FIndependent that these links had been
OL,8,Fraised in Mandelson's vetting process
OL,9,Fand resulted in it not being granted.
OL,11,FAsked by the Guardian in February 2025
OL,12,Fabout his links to China, Mandelson
OL,13,Fsaid: "I have more important things to
OL,14,Fdeal with just now than your
OL,15,Fpropaganda, and I am making no
OL,16,Fcomment."
