OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FGovernment guidance says "the vetting
OL,7,Fclearance officer is not there to make
OL,8,Fmoral judgements about your
OL,9,Fexperiences or circumstances. Their
OL,10,Frole is to assess any potential
OL,11,Fsecurity risks. It is essential
OL,12,Ftherefore that you are open and honest
OL,13,Fat all stages of the interview
OL,14,Fprocess."
OL,16,FClearance may be "refused, or
OL,17,Fsubsequently withdrawn" if it later
OL,18,Femerges that an applicant lied or
OL,19,Fwithheld information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
