OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FTypically, individuals can fail
OL,7,Fdeveloped vetting for three reasons:
OL,9,FITV News understands Mandelson denies
OL,10,Fhaving prior knowledge that he had
OL,11,Ffailed security vetting.
OL,13,FCan a civil servant overrule the
OL,14,Fadvice of UK Security Vetting?
OL,16,FThe prime minister said he was
OL,17,F"furious" at having not been told
OL,18,FMandelson had failed security vetting.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/19
