OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FHis official spokesperson insisted
OL,7,Fnobody in No 10 was told Mandelson had
OL,8,Ffailed his security vetting, despite
OL,9,Frepeated requests for "assurances".
OL,11,FThis anger led to the sacking of top
OL,12,FForeign Office civil servant Olly
OL,13,FRobbins on Thursday night.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV News on Friday, Chief
OL,16,FSecretary to the Prime Minister,
OL,17,FDarren Jones, described the overulling
OL,18,Fof the vetting decision as a "failure
OL,19,Fof the state".
OL,26,@qD@WOUqD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/19
