OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FHe said: "Your viewers, as much as I,
OL,7,Fwill be astonished to know there are a
OL,8,Fsmall number of organisations that are
OL,9,Fallowed to ignore security advice when
OL,10,Fvetting individuals.
OL,12,F"I put an end to that practice
OL,13,Fimmediately last night."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/19
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
