OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FSpeaking on BBC Radio Four's World at
OL,7,FOne, Ciaran Martin, a close friend of
OL,8,FRobbins and former head of the
OL,9,FNational Cyber Security Centre, said:
OL,10,F"If an appointment has already been
OL,11,Fannounced, as in this case, you're
OL,12,Fpresented with an analysis of the
OL,13,Frisks and a handling plan.
OL,15,F"The job of the (permanent sec) is to
OL,16,Fsay this risk is manageable and
OL,17,Ftherefore we should go ahead, or not.
