OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1776525067
OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,F"The one thing you never do is tell
OL,7,Fministers of any kind because
OL,8,Fotherwise the system would collapse...
OL,9,Fnobody would undertake vetting."
OL,11,FHowever, former British military
OL,12,Fintelligence Colonel Phillip Ingram,
OL,13,Fwho has experience of vetting
OL,14,Fprocesses, disputes this. Ingram told
OL,15,FITV News that withholding the result
OL,16,Fof the vetting process from ministers
OL,17,Fand the prime minister is "not normal
OL,18,Fprocess".
