OL,3,CWhat is the developed security vetting
OL,4,CPeter Mandelson reportedly failed?
OL,6,FHe believes a high-profile case like
OL,7,FMandelson failing the procedure would
OL,8,Fhave been flagged to the then foreign
OL,9,Fsecretary David Lammy.
OL,11,FNo 10 denies this was the case.
